              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I have the same problem. We are 5 friends playing and the 2 who entered the game previously do not have the error and can see the online skins, me (that I downloaded the game yesterday) and other two friends that purchased the game yesterday can’t see online skins. Its not a problem with the link between the skin and the account, because we can see it the game launcher. Basically the game can’t get online skins from the Minecraft servers. And no software, firewall or antivirus are in the middle."
